            "format": "basic_html",
            "processed": "<p><a href=\"https://github.com/kreshuklab/plant-seg/blob/master/plantseg\">PlantSeg</a><span> is a tool for cell instance aware segmentation in densely packed 3D volumetric images. The pipeline uses a two stages segmentation strategy (Neural Network + Segmentation). The pipeline is tuned for plant cell tissue acquired with confocal and light sheet microscopy. Pre-trained models are provided.</span></p>",
